<br>
One day, my friend was approached by a former guildmate he knew pretty well.  The old guild had broken up, but this was one of the people he had played with since the begining.  The former guildmate said that he was tired of his account and was about to quit playing, and was he perhaps interested in swapping accounts to renew both their interests in the game?<br>
<br>
It sounded like a reasonable deal, and my friend agreed.  He had a lot of fun with his new character, and spent about 5 months on him.<br>
<br>
Well, luclin is coming up soon, and recently, my friend suddenly found his password no longer working.  He logs in on his second account and finds this character he'd been playing on, claiming that he hadn't been playing for over a year, and that when he tried to log in, found that his account had been hacked a while back.  Fortunately, this player had been finally able to get control of his account back, recently, almost a year since he had been played it.  It seems that the account my friend had traded for did not even belong to the person who he traded to.<br>
<br>
So, please, if anyone, ANYONE, even trusted buddies, ever asks if you want to trade accounts, just realize that the risk is that you will have to start over from scratch at some point.  If that's an acceptable risk for you, go for it, if not, just say no. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/ukatiaangelfury.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Katia Angelfury</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Regular Poster</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(11/27/01 9:00:04 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=629.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.home.net/sirastral/profile.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Keep yer derned passwerds to yerself, okie?</span><hr size=1> doh <p><FONT color="RED"><B><A href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=6850" target="new">Katia Angelfury</A> / Astrel Angelfire</FONT></B><BR>
